  "title": "Project Engineer (BMS, Construction/M&E)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Manage and oversee BMS projects in <strong>construction and M&amp;E</strong> sectors from planning to execution.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with clients, consultants, and contractors to ensure project requirements are met.</li>\n  <li>Supervise the installation, testing, and commissioning of BMS systems on construction sites.</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with M&amp;E standards, construction safety regulations, and project specifications.</li>\n  <li>Provide technical support, troubleshoot system issues, and conduct system handovers.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Electrical, Mechanical, or Building Services Engineering.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years of experience in <strong>BMS-focused projects</strong> within <strong>construction/M&amp;E industry.</strong></li>\n  <li>Familiar with <strong>BMS systems (e.g., Siemens, Schneider, Honeywell, etc.).</strong></li>\n  <li>Strong project management, coordination, and problem-solving skills.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701<br>\nRegistration: R1326740</p>",
